data.description:
This charming home in St Mary's offers a lot of great features. It has 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, with the owner's suite conveniently located on the main level. The bathroom has been recently updated with a remodeled shower. The open kitchen overlooks a private back yard and includes a breakfast bar and stainless-steel appliances.
The cozy great room is accentuated by a brick fireplace, perfect for relaxing and enjoying some quality time. Upstairs, you'll find two spacious bedrooms with brand new carpet. One of the bedrooms can be used as a bonus room, providing flexibility and versatility in its functionality.
You can also enjoy the outdoors on the front and back covered porches, both of which have a charming tin roof. The lot size is almost half an acre, providing ample space. There is even an area for RV and camper parking, as well as a large, detached workshop for your convenience.
Overall, this home offers a cozy and inviting atmosphere, with modern updates and plenty of space both inside and outside.
